text:
Amber Tamblyn Gives Birth to First Child Amber Tamblyn Welcomes Her First Child With Husband David Cross February 21, 2017 by Monica Sisavat 516 Shares 
Congratulations are in order for Amber Tamblyn and David Cross â€” the couple recently welcomed their first child, a baby girl, and announced her arrival on Instagram on Tuesday. Along with a cute clip of her baby's tiny foot peeking out of a pink blanket, the Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants star, wrote, "David and I are proud to announce the birth of our daughter, Dauphinoise Petunia Brittany Scheherazade Von Funkinstein Mustard Witch RBG Cross Tamblyn-Bey jr. #TheFutureIsFemale" While the proud parents did not reveal any more information, we have a strong feeling that's not the little one's real name. Amber and her comedian husband tied the knot in 2012 after four years of dating. Feb 21, 2017 at 11:45am PST Related:
